Ga go na dinepe dipe tsa gago le dividio tse di tla phimolwang, mme ga di na go tlhola di bonala mo sedirisong.

resources.residConnectUpsellFlyoutText: O ka kgona go bona dinepe le dibidio mo didirisweng tsa gago, le dineteweke tsa tsalano tsotlhe mo lefelong le le lengwe. Gore o simolole, tlhomamisa gore o golagane le Inthanete.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_EmptySourceView: Dinepe tsa gago tsotlhe di fitlhilwe. Go bontsha tse dingwe, fetola dithulaganyo tsa gago.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_GenericDevice:
Sediriso sa Dinepe se go bontsha dinepe le dividio go tswa mo didirisweng tsotlhe mo lefelong le le lengwe.

Go bona dinepe le dividio go tswa go PC e nngwe, ya kwa PC eo, ya go, SkyDrive.com/windowsgo laisolola le go tsenya Microsoft SkyDrive, saenela go tsena ka akhaonte ya gago ya Microsoft, o bo o tlhomamisa gore o tshwaya thulaganyo ya Tsaya difaele tsa gago go tswa gope fela mo thulaganyong ya .
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Device: Fa o na le dipe, tlhomamisa gore o di akareditse mo laeboraring ya gago ya Dinepe {{%1}}.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Service: Tsenya dinepe dingwe mo akhaonto ya gago gore o simolole.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_SkyDrive:
SkyDrive e go naya lefelo le le sa duelelweng la go boloka dinepe, dividio le ditokumente gore o kgone go di bula go tswa gope fela.

E ya go SkyDrive.com go simolola. Dinepe le dividio dipe tse o di bolokang moo di tla bontshiwa fano.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_PicturesLibrary:
Go simolola, golaganya sediriswa (khamera, founo, mogatlana wa USB, jalo jalo), o bo o romelateng kgotsa o kopololela dinepe le dividio mo laeboraring ya gago ya Ditshwantsho

Fa e le gore o setse o na le dinepe kgotsa dividio mo PC eno, tlhomamisa gore di mo laeboraring ya gago ya Ditshwantsho. O ka kgona go laola laeborari ya gago ya Ditshwantsho go tswa mo Windows Explorer.
